name: Cindy Prado
description:
Cindy Prado is an American model and social media influencer.

Another 200-step TI. Trained on 20 (out of an initial selection of 35) images taken from her Instagram account, which I later upscaled to remove imperfections. Fixed learning rate of 0.004.

If you get saturated results, remember that you can reduce the embedding's weight in your prompt! Try something like "(cindypr4d0:0.99)", see if the pics look better.

Curious about my work process? I have summarized it here.

Appreciate my work? You can buy me a coffee!
